(14, NULL, NULL, 'Dormitories', 'dormitories', '<p>The campus of the Federal State Educational Budgetary Institution of Higher Education &ldquo;MIREA &ndash; Russian Technological University&rdquo; has a number of student dormitories for nonresident students, postgraduates, doctoral students, and trainees.<br />\nForeign students live in dormitories 1 and 5.<br />\nThe cost of accommodation ranges from 863 rubles to 5,289 rubles per month.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Dormitory 1</strong>&nbsp;is located at the address: Moscow, 86 Vernadsky Avenue, bldg. 1 (the nearest metro station is Yugo-Zapadnaya).<br />\n<br />\nThe living space of the dormitory is 8,359.6 sq.m.<br />\nThe dormitory caters for 1,161 people. It is a 14-storey panel building.<br />\nIt is a block-type dormitory with separate rooms forming small apartments (2 rooms each) with a separate sanitary unit and a shower room. The kitchen is for the common use of those residing on the same floor.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"Проспект Вернадского 2\" src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/5f1/IMG_20190731_120507_min.jpg\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" />&nbsp;<img alt=\"Проспект Вернадского 4\" src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/3c8/IMG_20190731_120055_min.jpg\" style=\"height:200px; width:300px\" /></p>\n\n<p>The dormitory is equipped with a video surveillance system (CCTV), and a fire alarm.<br />\nEach room has a wardrobe, a bed, a bedside table, a shelf, a desk, a chair, a couple of 220V sockets, the bedding, a mattress, a pillow, a blanket, a bedspread, and the bed linen.<br />\nThe dormitory has a room for self-study, a guest room, a bicycle parking, a drawing room, a library, an art studio, a dance room and the Internet network.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Dormitory 5</strong>&nbsp;is located at the address: Moscow, 36 11th Parkovaya St. (the nearest metro station is Pervomayskaya).<br />\n<br />\nThe living space of the dormitory is 6,433.1 sq.m.<br />\nThe dormitory caters for 800 people. It is a block-type building.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/a24/4_1.jpg\" style=\"width:300px\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/e06/4_2.jpg\" style=\"width:300px\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/0b4/4_3.jpg\" style=\"width:300px\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/9c4/XSdTZui_dDo.jpg\" style=\"width:300px\" /></p>\n\n<p>The block type dormitory has separate rooms organized in small apartments (blocks of 2 rooms each) with a separate sanitary unit and a shower room. There are two kitchens on each floor.<br />\nThe dormitory is equipped with the access control and management system, and the voice notification system operated in Russian; video surveillance system; and a fire alarm.<br />\nEach room has a wardrobe, a bed, a bedside table, a shelf, a writing desk, 220V sockets, the bedding, a mattress (90x200 cm), a pillow (70x70 cm), a blanket (150x200 cm), the bed linen, and a bedspread.<br />\nThe dormitory has a dining room, a room for self-study, a guest room, a recreation room, a storage room, a laundry room, an ironing room, a gym, an Internet network, a bicycle parking and a room for drying clothes.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>In order to ensure the safety of students in the dormitories, there is access control, and 24-hour video surveillance.<br />\nThe dormitories have automatic fire alarms.<br />\nAll premises are equipped with fire extinguishers.<br />\nA new type of a smoke exhaust system was installed.<br />\nAccess to the territory of dormitories is not allowed without an ID.</strong></p>\n', '1'),
(15, NULL, NULL, 'Graduate Employment', 'graduate-employment', '<p>Assistance in the employment of students and graduates of the MIREA &ndash; Russian Technological University is based on the Career Center of RTU MIREA.</p>\n\n<p>The Career Center of RTU MIREA is a structural unit of the Russian Technological University created to assist employment and create jobs for students and graduates, provide information on jobs and offer advisory support in building their successful careers. The Career Center divisions operate in the University three main campuses.</p>\n\n<p>The Career Center is an opportunity to get a prestigious, interesting and well-paid job, receive further education and training, implement young people&rsquo;s business ideas, which by far is not all that the Center is to offer!</p>\n\n<p>The main goal of the Career Center is to create favorable conditions for the effective employment of the graduates. To this end, the Center is resolving various issues, specifically</p>\n\n<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; provides information to the students on the situation in the labor market and employment prospects;</p>\n\n<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; gathers information about potential jobs for students and creates a database of job opportunities;</p>\n\n<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; establishes partner relationships with the authorities, government agencies and commercial organizations to organize of students on-the-job training and graduate employment;</p>\n\n<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; organizes joint presentations, workshops, meetings, and seminars with employers.</p>\n\n<p>Over 80% of the graduates willing to find a job during the first year after their graduation succeeds in getting employment.</p>\n\n<p>As of 5 December 2019, according to the Department of Labor and Employment of the City of Moscow, only 7 graduates applied for jobs to the Moscow Employment Center, which is less than 0.2% of the total number of 2019 graduates.</p>\n\n<p>Our University successfully cooperates with over 40 major enterprises. Specialized departments participate in the educational process: employees of partner companies conduct lectures and seminars, workshops, supervise work on diplomas and term papers, assist in the on-the-job training and internships, engage students in various projects, and research and development.</p>\n\n<p>The Career Center collaborates with more than 600 Russian and foreign companies and enterprises.</p>\n\n<p>More detailed information and current job opportunities are available on the RTU MIREA Career Center website:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://career.mirea.ru/\">http://career.mirea.ru</a>.</p>\n', '1'),
