sities in Russia 2019 (RAEX)</a></p>\n\n			<p><a href=\"https://raex-rr.com/education/universities/rating_of_IT_univercities\">Top 50 IT universities 2019 (RAEX)</a></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>64</p>\n\n			<p>21</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td colspan=\"2\">\n			<p><a href=\"https://www.elibrary.ru/org_compare.asp\">Higher educational institutions of the Russian Federation, citation index in the RSCI (as of 31.10.2019)</a></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>64</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td colspan=\"2\">\n			<p><a href=\"http://www.webometrics.info/en\">Webometrics (among the universities of the Russian Federation) as of 31.10.2019</a></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>39</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td colspan=\"2\">\n			<p><a href=\"http://eurochambres.org/sidebar/detail.php?CODE=ares-2019-russian-federation&amp;clear_cache=Y\">Academic Ranking of World Universities-European Standard ARES-2019</a>&nbsp;(ARES-2019 Russian Federation)</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p>86</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', '4'),
(31, NULL, NULL, 'International Relations Department', 'international-relations-department', '<blockquote>\n<h1><strong>International Cooperation Department</strong></h1>\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3><strong>GENERAL INFORMATION</strong></h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/408/RTU_1058_Ushakova-Anna-Dmitrievna.JPG\"><img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/408/RTU_1058_Ushakova-Anna-Dmitrievna.JPG\" style=\"float:left; height:240px; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px; width:160px\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Anna Dmitrievna Ushakova</strong></p>\n\n<p>Inspector of the International Cooperation Department</p>\n\n<p>Address: 78 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Building A, Office A-304<br />\nPhone: +7 499 215-65-65 ext. 1092<br />\n<br />\nE-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:ushakova@mirea.ru\">ushakova@mirea.ru</a></p>\n\n<p>The International Cooperation Department deals with a wide range of issues and objectives to ensure partnership and interaction of the University with foreign and international organizations, interacts with cultural centers, consulates and embassies of different countries. This activity is aimed to enhance cooperation, attract international students, and raise the prestige of the University.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>The key objectives of the Department are:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>to develop programs of international cooperation, expand international partnership, interact with foreign universities and scientific and research organizations, participate in international associations;</li>\n	<li>to monitor contracts and agreements of the University with foreign partners in the field of international scientific activities, academic mobility of teaching staff and researchers;</li>\n	<li>to develop international academic mobility and enhance the academic reputation of the University;</li>\n	<li>to implement double degree programs, maintain academic exchanges and organize internship and externship training;</li>\n	<li>to assist the departments of the University in obtaining foreign grants and to conclude contracts;</li>\n	<li>to obtain visas, collect documents for employees of the University for business trips outside the Russian Federation;</li>\n	<li>to prepare orders for secondment of employees of the University;</li>\n	<li>to register and store document files of the University employees traveling abroad;</li>\n	<li>to assist University employees in obtaining passports at the consular department of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Russian Federation</li>\n	<li>to receive foreign delegations, organize international conferences, exhibitions, forums, research projects, and to participate in such events;</li>\n	<li>to prepare information, reference and reporting materials on the international activities of the University.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>STAFF</strong></h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/408/RTU_1058_Ushakova-Anna-Dmitrievna.JPG\"><img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/408/RTU_1058_Ushakova-Anna-Dmitrievna.JPG\" style=\"float:left; height:240px; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px; width:160px\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Anna Dmitrievna Ushakova</strong></p>\n\n<p>Inspector of the International Cooperation Department</p>\n\n<p>Address: 78 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Building A, Office A-304<br />\nPhone: +7 499 215-65-65 ext. 1092<br />\n<br />\nE-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:ushakova@mirea.ru\">ushakova@mirea.ru</a></p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/9d1/RTU_1080_SHabasheva-Ekaterina-Romanovna.JPG\"><img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/9d1/RTU_1080_SHabasheva-Ekaterina-Romanovna.JPG\" style=\"float:left; height:240px; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px; width:160px\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Ekaterina Romanovna Shabasheva</strong></p>\n\n<p>Inspector of the International Cooperation Department</p>\n\n<p>Address: 78 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Building A, Office A-304<br />\nPhone: +7 499 215-65-65 ext. 1084<br />\nE-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:shabasheva@mirea.ru\">shabasheva@mirea.ru</a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<h1><strong>Department for work with foreign students</strong></h1>\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3><strong>GENERAL INFORMATION</strong></h3>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/688/RTU_2157_-Burtseva-Irina-YUrevna.JPG\"><img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/688/RTU_2157_-Burtseva-Irina-YUrevna.JPG\" style=\"float:left; height:240px; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px; width:160px\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Irina Yurievna Burtseva</strong></p>\n\n<p>Head of the Department for work with foreign students</p>\n\n<p>Address: 78 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Building A, Office A-304<br />\nPhone: +7 499 215-65-65 ext. 1082<br />\nE-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:burceva@mirea.ru\">burceva@mirea.ru</a></p>\n\n<p>The Department for work with foreign students deals with a wide range of issues and objectives relating to the stay of foreign nationals in the Russian Federation, interacts with the Ministry of Internal Affairs and the Main Directorate of the Ministry of Internal Affairs on migration, registration, and visa regime. The employees of the Department are professionals in their area of work, speak foreign languages (English, Spanish, French, Chinese), are experienced in working with international students.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>The key objectives of the Department are:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>to issue invitations to foreign citizens for obtaining visas in the host country and the subsequent entry into the Russian Federation;</li>\n	<li>to register international students on migration;</li>\n	<li>to issue multiple-entry visas for international students, providing visa support to accompanying family members;</li>\n	<li>to registration of a voluntary medical insurance policy;</li>\n	<li>to monitor compliance with the rules of stay of foreign nationals in the territory of the Russian Federation;</li>\n	<li>to register and store personal data of international students;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>to monitor the validity of visas, registrations and medical insurance of foreign students;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>to participate in the admission procedure of foreign applicants;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>to regular monitor the amendments in the migration laws of the Russian Federation informing students about the changes introduced;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>to assist international students in adapting to the new educational and socio-cultural environment;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>to prepare information materials for foreign applicants, full-time students and students of training courses on the rules of stay in the Russian Federation;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>to interact with the structural divisions of the University on organizational issues;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>to cooperate with international departments of Russian universities on respective issues;&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>to interact with consulates and embassies of foreign states whose nationals are studying at the University.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>STAFF</strong></h3>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/688/RTU_2157_-Burtseva-Irina-YUrevna.JPG\"><img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/688/RTU_2157_-Burtseva-Irina-YUrevna.JPG\" style=\"float:left; height:240px; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px; width:160px\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Irina Yurievna Burtseva</strong></p>\n\n<p>Head of the Department for work with foreign students</p>\n\n<p>Address: 78 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Building A, Office A-304<br />\nPhone: +7 499 215-65-65 ext. 1082<br />\nE-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:burceva@mirea.ru\">burceva@mirea.ru</a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/e24/RTU_1091_Dvurechenskaya-Veronika-YUrevna.JPG\"><img src=\"https://www.mirea.ru/upload/medialibrary/e24/RTU_1091_Dvurechenskaya-Veronika-YUrevna.JPG\" style=\"float:left; height:240px; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px; width:160px\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Veronika Yurievna Dvurechenskaya</strong></p>\n\n<p>Inspector of the Department for work with foreign students</p>\n\n<p>Address: 78 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Building A, Office A-304<br />\nPhone: +7 499 215-65-65 ext. 1083<br />\nE-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:dvurechenskaya@mirea.ru\">dvurechenskaya@mirea.ru</a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', '4');

