yle=\"float:left; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Natalia Alexandrovna Bragina</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Doctor of Chemical Sciences, Professsor</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Address: 86 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Office P-102</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Telephone:&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+74952460555ext.246\">+7 495 246-05-55 ext. 246</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:bragina@mirea.ru\">bragina@mirea.ru</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&nbsp;Reception hours</em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monday 12:00 a.m. &mdash; 3:00 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Wednesday 11:00 a.m. &mdash; 2:00 p.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Deputy Director for Communication with Applicants</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://english.mirea.ru/upload/resize_cache/iblock/051/96_300_1/RTU_0745_Pastukhova_ZHanna_YUrevna.jpg\" style=\"float:left; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zhanna Yurievna Pastukhova</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Candidate of Chemical Sciences</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Address: 86 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Office К-121</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Telephone:&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+74992156565ext.250\">+7 499 215-65-65 ext. 250</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Reception hours</em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tuesday 10:00 a.m. &mdash; 12:00 a.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Deputy Director</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://english.mirea.ru/upload/resize_cache/iblock/935/96_300_1/RTU_6316_Korolkova_Natalya_Anatolevna.jpg\" style=\"float:left; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Natalya Anatolyevna Korol&rsquo;kova</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Address: 86 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Office P-118b</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Telephone:&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+74952460555ext.207\">+7 495 246-05-55 ext. 207</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:korolnat@mitht.ru\">korolnat@mitht.ru</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Reception hours</em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monday 10:00 a.m. &mdash; 5:00 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Tuesday 10:00 a.m. &md