(37, NULL, NULL, 'Institute Administration', 'institute-administration', '<p><strong>Director of the Institute</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://english.mirea.ru/upload/resize_cache/iblock/a40/96_300_1/RTU_5963_Vasilev_Andrey_Georgievich.jpg\" style=\"float:left; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Andrey Georgiyevich Vasilev</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Doctor of Physics and Mathematics</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Address: 78 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Office B-320</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Telephone:&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+74992156565ext.2001\">+7 499 215-65-65 ext. 2001</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:vasilev_a@mirea.ru\">vasilev_a@mirea.ru</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Reception hours</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monday 4:00 p.m. &ndash; 6:00 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Wednesday 4:00 p.m. &ndash; 7:00 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Friday 4:00 p.m. &ndash; 6:00 p.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Deputy Director</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://english.mirea.ru/upload/resize_cache/iblock/9a8/96_300_1/RTU_6043_Vorunichev_Dmitriy_Sergeevich.jpg\" style=\"float:left; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dmitry Sergeevich Vorunichev</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Address: 78 Vernadskogo Prospekt, Office B-413</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Telephone:&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+74992156565ext.2039\">+7 499 215-65-65 ext. 2039</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:vorunichev@mirea.ru\">vorunichev@mirea.ru</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Reception hours</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Monday 4:00 p.m. &ndash; 6:00 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Wednesday 4:00 p.m. &ndash; 6:00 p.m.</li>\r\n	<li>Friday 4:00 p.m. &ndash; 7:00 p.m.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Director for Teching Instructions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://english.mirea.ru/upload/resize_cache/iblock/6b9/96_300_1/RTU_5995_Nikishina_Elena_Evgenevna.jpg\" style=\"float:left; margin-left:10px; margin-right:10px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Elena Yevgenyevna Nikishina</strong></p>\r\